 over the course of their history, some of which have been the owners of the club, others have been honorary chairmen. Here is a complete list of Bologna chairmen from 1909 until the present day.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.federossoblu.net/it/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=118&Itemid=66|publisher=FedeRossoblu.net|title=Tutti I Presidenti del Bologna|date=13 October 2007}}</ref>\n<div style=\"font-size:100%\">\n{|\n|-\n|width=\"10\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!|Name\n!|Years\n|-\n|align=left|Louis Rauch\n|align=left|1909\u201310\n|-\n|align=left|Pio Borghesani\n|align=left|1910\n|-\n|align=left|Emilio Arnstein\n|align=left|1910\n|-\n|align=left|Domenico Gori\n|align=left|1910\u201312\n|-\n|align=left|Rodolfo Minelli\n|align=left|1912\u201315\n|-\n|align=left|Arturo Gazzoni <small>(''Honorary chairman'')</small>\n|align=left|1916\u201318\n|-\n|align=left|Rodolfo Minelli\n|align=left|1918\u201319\n|-\n|align=left|Cesare Medica\n|align=left|1919\u201321\n|-\n|align=left|Angelo Sbarberi\n|align=left|1921\u201322\n|-\n|align=left|Antonio Turri\n|align=left|1922\n|-\n|align=left|Ruggero Mur\u00e8 <small>(''Honorary chairman'')</small>\n|align=left|1923\n|-\n|align=left|Enrico Masetti\n|align=left|1923\u201325\n|-\n|align=left|Paolo Graziani\n|align=left|1925\u201328\n|-\n|align=left|Gianni Bonaveri\n|align=left|1928\u201334\n|-\n|align=left|Renato Dall'Ara\n|align=left|1934\u201364\n|-\n|align=left|Luigi Goldoni\n|align=left|1964\u201368\n|-\n|align=left|Raimondo Venturi\n|align=left|1968\u201370\n|}\n|width=\"30\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!|Name\n!|Years\n|-\n|align=left|Filippo Montanari\n|align=left|1970\u201372\n|-\n|align=left|Luciano Conti\n|align=left|1972\u201379\n|-\n|align=left|Tommaso Fabbretti\n|align=left|1979\u201383\n|-\n|align=left|Giuseppe Brizzi\n|align=left|1983\u201385\n|-\n|align=left|Luigi \"Gino\" Corioni\n|align=left|1985\